            "Visual_LandingPage_Purpose2_Text": "Intense color cells instantly highlight exceptional values, allowing for immediate investigation of spikes or drops in data.",
            "Visual_LandingPage_Purpose3_Title": "Comparative Analysis",
            "Visual_LandingPage_Purpose3_Text": "By using the category feature, compare seasonal trends between different departments, regions, or product lines.",
            "Visual_LandingPage_Purpose4_Title": "Data Density",
            "Visual_LandingPage_Purpose4_Text": "Perfect for visualizing high-frequency data where traditional line charts might become too cluttered"
